OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FWater companies could now face new
OL,7,Flegal challenges over sewage
OL,8,Fdischarges, campaigners have said,
OL,9,Ffollowing a "landmark" Supreme Court
OL,10,Fruling.
OL,12,FThe ruling involves a long running
OL,13,Fdispute between the Manchester Ship
OL,14,FCanal Company (MSCC) and United
OL,15,FUtilities about discharges of foul
OL,16,Fwater contaminated with untreated
OL,17,Fsewage into the canal.
