OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FThe canal runs for over 35 miles from
OL,7,Fjust east of Salford Quays to the
OL,8,FMersey Estuary at Eastham on the
OL,9,FWirral, and United Utilities sewerage
OL,10,Fnetwork includes around 100 outfalls
OL,11,Ffrom which material emanating from
OL,12,Fsewers, sewage treatment works and
OL,13,Fpumping stations is discharged into
OL,14,Fthe water.
OL,16,FWhen operating within its hydraulic
OL,17,Fcapacity, the discharges are of
OL,18,Fsurface water or treated effluent, but
OL,19,Fwhen the system's hydraulic capacity
OL,20,Fis exceeded at least some foul water
OL,21,Fis discharged.
