OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FIt had previously been ruled by the
OL,7,FHigh Court and Court of Appeal that
OL,8,Fwater companies couldn't be sued by
OL,9,Fprivate individuals or businesses over
OL,10,Fsewage dumping, so MSCC took an appeal
OL,11,Fagainst those rulings to the Supreme
OL,12,FCourt.
OL,14,FOn social media, former singer Feargal
OL,15,FSharkey, who now campaigns against
OL,16,Fpollution described the ruling as
OL,17,F"massive" adding that it "opens the
OL,18,Fway for 1,000s of claims by fishing
OL,19,Fclubs, swimmers, riparian owners
OL,20,Fagainst water companies".
