OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FDuring a two day hearing in March
OL,7,F2023, the court was asked to decide
OL,8,Fwhether MSCC, which owns the beds and
OL,9,Fbanks of the canal, could bring a
OL,10,Fclaim in nuisance or trespass when the
OL,11,Fcanal is polluted by discharges of
OL,12,Ffoul water from outfalls, which are
OL,13,Fmaintained by United Utilities.
OL,15,FIn its ruling on Tuesday 2 July 2024,
OL,16,FThe Supreme Court unanimously allowed
OL,17,Fthe Canal Company's appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
