OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,FIt holds that the 1991 Act does not
OL,7,Fprevent the Canal Company from
OL,8,Fbringing a claim in nuisance or
OL,9,Ftrespass when the canal is polluted by
OL,10,Fdischarges of foul water from United
OL,11,FUtilities' outfalls, even if there has
OL,12,Fbeen no negligence or deliberate
OL,13,Fmisconduct.
OL,15,FA United Utilities spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"We are considering the implications
OL,17,Fof the Supreme Court's ruling and the
OL,18,Fclarification of the circumstances in
OL,19,Fwhich private owners could bring
OL,20,Fproceedings in respect of discharges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
