OL,3,CSewage companies could face new legal
OL,4,Cbids after 'landmark' ruling
OL,6,F"We understand and share people's
OL,7,Fconcerns about the need for change and
OL,8,Fwe have already made an early start on
OL,9,Fan ambitious proposed #3 billion
OL,10,Fprogramme to improve over 400 storm
OL,11,Foverflows across the North West which
OL,12,Fwould cut spills by 60% over the
OL,13,Fdecade to 2030.
OL,15,F"These proposals form part of our
OL,16,Fbusiness plan which is currently under
OL,17,Fconsideration as part of Ofwat's price
OL,18,Freview process."
